meta.description: Daily lead pulling from PropertyRadar API with multi-broker support, ZIP rotation, and stop-when-known deduplication

parameters.query: SELECT id, company_name, daily_lead_capacity FROM brokers WHERE status = 'active' ORDER BY company_name

=SELECT upsert_broker_daily_stat(
  p_broker_id := '{{ $json.broker_id }}'::uuid,
  p_session_id := '{{ $json.session_id }}',
  p_status := 'in_progress'
) as stat_id

=SELECT id, broker_id, market_name, zip_code, priority 
FROM broker_territories 
WHERE broker_id = '{{ $json.broker_id }}' 
  AND active = true 
ORDER BY priority DESC, zip_code

parameters.jsonBody: ={{ JSON.stringify({Criteria: [{name: 'ZipFive', value: [$json.current_zip]}, {name: 'Age', value: [[62, null]]}, {name: 'AvailableEquity', value: [[150000, null]]}, {name: 'EquityPercent', value: [[40, null]]}, {name: 'isSameMailingOrExempt', value: [1]}, {name: 'PropertyType', value: [{name: 'PType', value: ['SFR', 'DPX', 'TPX', 'FPX', 'CND']}]}, {name: 'AVM', value: [[400000, 3000000]]}, {name: 'CLTV', value: [[null, 60]]}]}) }}

parameters.query:
=SELECT upsert_lead_from_radar(
  radar_id := '{{ $json.radar_id }}',
  property_address := '{{ $json.property_address }}',
  property_city := '{{ $json.property_city }}',
  property_state := '{{ $json.property_state }}',
  property_zip := '{{ $json.property_zip }}',
  property_value := {{ $json.property_value }},
  estimated_equity := {{ $json.estimated_equity }},
  age := {{ $json.age }},
  owner_occupied := {{ $json.owner_occupied }},
  apn := '{{ $json.apn }}',
  county_fips := '{{ $json.county_fips }}',
  addr_hash := '{{ $json.addr_hash }}',
  assigned_broker_id := '{{ $json.assigned_broker_id }}'::uuid,
  radar_property_data := '{{ JSON.stringify($json.radar_property_data) }}'::jsonb,
  radar_api_version := '{{ $json.radar_api_version }}'
) as lead_id

=SELECT upsert_broker_daily_stat(
  p_broker_id := '{{ $json.broker_id }}'::uuid,
  p_increment_leads := 1,
  p_current_zip := '{{ $json.current_zip }}'
) as stat_id

=UPDATE source_bookmarks 
SET last_page_fetched = {{ $json.last_page + 1 }},
    updated_at = NOW()
WHERE id = '{{ $json.bookmark_id }}'::uuid
RETURNING *
